channel.title: I think the world will end very soon
channel.description:
I think our time on earth is coming to an end. Any particular reason? No. A series of news articles, perhaps, that have no real connection, have connected in my brain, and the only logical answer is that the apocalypse is coming.
No war has purpose, and there is no purpose without war. Unfortunately we have weapons that kill so efficiently that war itself will soon become obsolete.
The dust particles that are left over from my body will collide with the dust particles of what is left of your body, in a gesture that says unmistakably, I [b]told you so[/b].
